title: [1508521049] Matilda and The Ramsay Bunch is Back!
description:
Tilly and the gang (include Gordon of course) are back for a whole new series.  Fridays at 7.45am on CBBC.
Subscribe for weekly cooking videos. 

If you liked this clip check out the rest of Gordon's channels:
